---
title: Chicken Pot Pie Stew with Crusty Garlic Toasts
description: Classic chicken pot pie soothes the soul, but who has the time? This meal combines all the comforting flavours you love in a hearty stew loaded with chicken and vegetables, and made in half the time! Soak up all the delicious broth with crusty garlic toasts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-pot-pie-stew-f76f36f1.jpg
